            include the staff the church pays to run the various warships. While the actual vehicles of the Sigmarines (both ground and air vehicles) are limited to only sigmarines. Thus the remaining 22,217 Sigmarines in
            each chapter are devoted to handleing the various air support, shuttles, tanks, ground transports, etc. As well as maitence positions and other high ranks with in the church.
